{"tid":782969,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁美芬要求立法禁止為提倡港獨人士提供宣傳平台","createTime":"2018-08-17T07:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T08:05:27.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e861120fd287b32e52456bcb4e7daa43ebd3b8","tid":782969,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:47:06.000Z","msg":"經民聯立法會議員梁美芬，聯同部分法律界人士，要求政府堵塞法律漏洞，指現時未有法律，禁止任何人為提倡港獨的人士，提供宣傳平台或場所。她不希望港獨有如細菌般、以任何形式蔓延，否則會毒害下一代和整個香港。她批評反對派缺乏政治智慧，只強調尊重言論及新聞自由，但相關自由並非無限。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬又指，《基本法》第23條立法，在2003年後變成禁忌，期望港人珍惜可以自行就第23條立法的權利，呼籲民主派重新審視現今情況，做好相關立法工作，並拒絕與港獨人士糾結在一起，才符合香港法律和政治文化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1025031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D1025031&d=pA37NK4D6xUPDCHRwULZb%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=9e05dc6c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1025031</a>"},{"pid":"d8891720c3c3db49e6f9ad72e80b4fa22a28b012","tid":782969,"uid":60281,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:47:57.000Z","msg":"係咪要告youtube?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2576f9972b87aa464673cd183f3ad8e9ae9763","tid":782969,"uid":10680,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:48:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c919ef46e39f517e546b57acb9a0c7fcc327dba","tid":782969,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:49:01.000Z","msg":"期望港人珍惜可以自行就第23條立法的權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a879affa72f26c3059430aacf9070779d3359b1","tid":782969,"uid":93784,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:50:05.000Z","msg":"平台: 689 facebook <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0674333df864285c8d1c15b93